# Cloud sync (optional) — without these set on the Vercel project, the app
# just runs local-only exactly as before (Perfil → Sincronización shows
# "no configurado").
#
# 1. Provision a Postgres database: Vercel dashboard → your project → Storage
#    → Create Database → Postgres (backed by Neon). Connecting it to the
#    project auto-injects DATABASE_URL — no need to set it manually here.
#
# 2. Set these two yourself in Vercel dashboard → Settings → Environment
#    Variables (Production + Preview):
AUTH_PIN=choose-a-pin
AUTH_SECRET=a-long-random-string
